%% Fluxo: Upload e Distribuição de Arquivo
%% Referência: docs/blueprint/07-critical_flows.md

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor Membro as Membro Familiar
    participant Web as Web Client<br/>(Next.js 16)
    participant API as Orquestrador<br/>(Rust + Axum 0.8)
    participant Redis as Redis 7<br/>(Fila)
    participant Worker as Media Worker<br/>(Rust + FFmpeg)
    participant SDK as Core SDK<br/>(Crypto + Chunk)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL 18<br/>(SQLx)
    participant S3 as StorageProvider<br/>(S3/R2)

    %% Upload
    Membro ->>+ Web: Seleciona arquivo e clica Upload
    Web ->>+ API: POST /files/upload (multipart, TLS 1.3)
    API ->> API: Valida JWT + permissões
    API ->>+ DB: INSERT files (status: processing)
    DB -->>- API: file_id
    API ->>+ Redis: Enfileira job {file_id, path}
    Redis -->>- API: OK
    API -->>- Web: 202 Accepted {file_id}
    Web -->>- Membro: "Processando..."

    %% Pipeline
    Redis ->>+ Worker: Consome job
    Worker ->> Worker: Analisa arquivo (resolução, formato, MIME)
    Worker ->> Worker: Otimiza: foto→WebP 1920px / vídeo→1080p H.265
    Worker ->> Worker: Gera preview (thumb 50KB / 480p 5MB)
    Worker ->> Worker: Extrai EXIF metadata

    Worker ->>+ SDK: Chunking + Encrypt
    SDK ->> SDK: Divide em chunks ~4MB + SHA-256
    SDK ->> SDK: Envelope encryption (master key → file key)
    SDK ->> SDK: AES-256-GCM cada chunk
    SDK ->> SDK: ConsistentHashRing → 3 nós destino
    SDK -->>- Worker: chunks_encrypted[]

    %% Distribuição
    loop Para cada chunk (3 réplicas)
        Worker ->>+ S3: PUT chunk (aws-sdk-s3)
        S3 -->>- Worker: OK
    end

    Worker ->>+ DB: INSERT chunks + chunk_replicas (transação)
    DB -->>- Worker: OK
    Worker ->>+ DB: INSERT manifest (chunks_json + file_key_encrypted)
    DB -->>- Worker: OK

    %% Replicar manifest em nós adicionais
    Worker ->>+ S3: PUT manifest (2+ nós)
    S3 -->>- Worker: OK

    Worker ->>+ DB: UPDATE files SET status = 'ready'
    DB -->>- Worker: OK
    Worker ->> Redis: PUBLISH file_ready {file_id}
    deactivate Worker

    %% Notificação
    Redis -->> API: file_ready event
    API -->> Web: SSE/Poll: arquivo pronto
    Web -->> Membro: Exibe thumbnail na galeria

    Note over Membro, S3: Arquivo processado, criptografado e distribuído com 3 réplicas por chunk
